Source: equalff
Maintainer: jhkst <jhkst@centrum.cz>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (=13), gcc, make
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/jhkst/equalff

Package: equalff
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libequalff0 (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: High-speed duplicate file finder
 Equalff is a high-speed duplicate file finder. It employs a unique
 algorithm, making it faster than other duplicate file finders for a
 single run.

Package: libequalff0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Core library for equalff duplicate file finder
 This package contains the shared library providing the core duplicate
 detection logic for the equalff utility.

Package: libequalff-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libequalff0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libequalff
 This package contains the headers and development files needed to build
 software against libequalff. 